      "summary": "提供 getInitProps 工具函数，根据字段配置中的 component 和 picker 属性查找对应的注入配置，实现字段组件的默认属性注入。",
      "tags": ["utility", "form-field", "dependency-injection"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:packages/antdv-next-pro/src/components/form/constants/index.ts",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "index.ts",
      "filePath": "packages/antdv-next-pro/src/components/form/constants/index.ts",
      "summary": "定义表单内置组件映射表（BaseComponentMap、componentMap）、组件名称联合类型（ComponentName）、类型提取器（GetComponentType）以及插槽键名等常量，是表单组件类型系统的基础。",
      "tags": ["constants", "组件映射", "form", "type-definition"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "通过 TypeScript 声明合并（declaration merging）对外暴露 ComponentMap 扩展接口，允许用户扩充自定义组件类型。"
    },
    {
